---
title: Quick Double Char Siu Beef Noodle Stir-Fry with Capsicum & Sesame Seeds
description: Time to get saucy tonight with a stir-fry. Not only is this double beef udon bowl chock-full of colour, flavour and texture, it comes together in four simple steps, so you'll be slurping your way to bliss in no time.
